activatable.description_zh: 缺少描述（在 github 中编辑）

activated.description: Array of ids of activated nodes.
activated.description_zh: 已激活节点的 ID 数组。

active-class.description: The class applied to the component when it is in an active state.
active-class.description_zh: 当组件处于活动状态时应用于组件的类。

active-color.description: The applied color when the component is in an active state.
active-color.description_zh: 组件处于活动状态时应用的颜色。

active-strategy.description: Affects how items with children behave when activated.leaf: Only leaf nodes (items without children) can be activated.independent: All nodes can be activated whether they have children or not.classic: Activating a parent node will cause all children to be activated.
active-strategy.description_zh: 影响有子节点的项目在激活时的行为。leaf：只能激活叶节点（没有子节点的项目）。independent：无论节点是否有子节点，都可以激活。classic：激活父节点将导致所有子节点被激活。

base-color.description: Sets the color of component when not focused.
base-color.description_zh: 设置未对焦时组件的颜色。

bg-color.description: Applies specified color to the control’s background. Used on components that also support the color prop. - supports utility colors (for example success or purple) or css color (#033 or rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5)). Find a list of built-in classes on the colors page.
bg-color.description_zh: 将指定的颜色应用于控件的背景。用于还支持颜色道具的组件。- 支持实用程序颜色（例如 success 或紫色）或 CSS 颜色（#033 或 rgba（255， 0， 0， 0.5））。在颜色页面上查找内置类的列表。

border.description: Designates the border-radius applied to the component. This can be xs, sm, md, lg, xl.
border.description_zh: 指定应用于组件的边框半径。这可以是 xs、sm、md、lg、xl。

collapse-icon.description_zh: 缺少描述（在 github 中编辑）

color.description: Applies specified color to the control - supports utility colors (for example success or purple) or css color (#033 or rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5)). Find a list of built-in classes on the colors page.
color.description_zh: 将指定的颜色应用于控件 - 支持实用程序颜色（例如 success 或紫色）或 css 颜色（#033 或 rgba（255， 0， 0， 0.5））。在颜色页面上查找内置类的列表。

density.description: Adjusts the vertical height used by the component.
density.description_zh: 调整元件使用的垂直高度。

disabled.description: Puts all children inputs into a disabled state.
disabled.description_zh: 将所有子项输入置于禁用状态。

elevation.description: Designates an elevation applied to the component between 0 and 24. You can find more information on the elevation page.
elevation.description_zh: 指定应用于组件的高程介于 0 和 24 之间。您可以在高程页面上找到更多信息。

expand-icon.description_zh: 缺少描述（在 github 中编辑）

height.description: Sets the height for the component.

item-children.description: Property on supplied items that contains its children.
item-children.description_zh: 包含其子项的所提供项的属性。

item-props.description: Props object that will be applied to each item component. true will treat the original object as raw props and pass it directly to the component.
item-props.description_zh: 将应用于每个项目组件的 Props 对象。true 会将原始对象视为原始 props，并将其直接传递给组件。

items.description: Can be an array of objects or strings. By default objects should have a title property, and can optionally have a props property containing any VListItem props, a value property to allow selection, and a children property containing more item objects. Keys to use for these can be changed with the item-title, item-value, item-props, and item-children props.
items.description_zh: 可以是对象或字符串的数组。默认情况下，对象应具有 title 属性，并且可以选择具有包含任何 VListItem 属性的 props 属性、允许选择的 value 属性以及包含更多项对象的 children 属性。可以使用 item-title、item-value、item-props 和 item-children props 更改用于这些属性的键。

item-title.description: Property on supplied items that contains its title.
item-title.description_zh: 包含其标题的所提供项目的属性。

item-type.description: Designates the key on the supplied items that is used for determining the nodes type.
item-type.description_zh: 指定所提供项上用于确定节点类型的键。

item-value.description: Property on supplied items that contains its value.
item-value.description_zh: 包含其值的已提供项的属性。

lines.description: Designates a minimum-height for all children v-list-item components. This prop uses line-clamp and is not supported in all browsers.
lines.description_zh: 指定所有子 v-list-item 组件的最小高度。此道具使用行钳，并非所有浏览器都支持。

mandatory.description: Forces at least one item to always be selected (if available).
mandatory.description_zh: 强制始终选择至少一个项目（如果可用）。

max-height.description: Sets the maximum height for the component.

max-width.description: Sets the maximum width for the component.

min-height.description: Sets the minimum height for the component.

min-width.description: Sets the minimum width for the component.

nav.description: An alternative styling that reduces v-list-item width and rounds the corners. Typically used with v-navigation-drawer.
nav.description_zh: 一种替代样式，可减小 V 列表项宽度并圆角。通常与 v-navigation-drawer 一起使用。

opened.description: An array containing the values of currently opened groups. Can be two-way bound with v-model:opened.
opened.description_zh: 包含当前打开的组的值的数组。可以与 v-model：opened 双向绑定。

open-strategy.description: Affects how items with children behave when expanded.multiple: Any number of groups can be open at once.single: Only one group at each level can be open, opening a group will cause others to close.list: Multiple, but all other groups will close when an item is selected.
open-strategy.description_zh: 影响具有子项的项目在展开时的行为。multiple：可以同时打开任意数量的组。single：每个级别只能打开一个组，打开一个组将导致其他组关闭。list：多个，但当选择某个项时，所有其他组都将关闭。

return-object.description: Changes the selection behavior to return the object directly rather than the value specified with item-value.
return-object.description_zh: 更改选择行为以直接返回对象，而不是使用 item-value 指定的值。

rounded.description: Designates the border-radius applied to the component. This can be 0, xs, sm, true, lg, xl, pill, circle, and shaped. Find more information on available border radius classes on the Border Radius page.
rounded.description_zh: 指定应用于组件的边框半径。这可以是 0、xs、sm、true、lg、xl、pill、circle 和 shaped。有关可用边框半径类的详细信息，请访问边框半径页面。

selectable.description_zh: 缺少描述（在 github 中编辑）

selected.description: An array containing the values of currently selected items. Can be two-way bound with v-model:selected.
selected.description_zh: 包含当前选定项的值的数组。可以与 v-model：sselected 进行双向绑定。

select-strategy.description: Affects how items with children behave when selected.leaf: Only leaf nodes (items without children) can be selected.independent: All nodes can be selected whether they have children or not.classic: Selecting a parent node will cause all children to be selected, parent nodes will be displayed as selected if all their descendants are selected. Only leaf nodes will be added to the model.
select-strategy.description_zh: 影响具有子节点的项在被选中时的行为方式。leaf：只能选择叶节点（没有子项）。independent：可以选择所有节点，无论它们是否有子节点。classic：选择父节点将导致所有子节点都被选中，如果选择父节点的所有后代，则父节点将显示为已选中。只有叶节点才会添加到模型中。

slim.description: Reduces horizontal spacing for badges, icons, tooltips, and avatars within slim list items to create a more compact visual representation.
slim.description_zh: 减小瘦列表项中锁屏提醒、图标、工具提示和头像的水平间距，以创建更紧凑的视觉表示形式。

tag.description: Specify a custom tag used on the root element.
tag.description_zh: 指定用于根元素的自定义标记。

theme.description: Specify a theme for this component and all of its children.
theme.description_zh: 为此组件及其所有子组件指定主题。

tile.description: Removes any applied border-radius from the component.
tile.description_zh: 从元件中移除任何应用的边框半径。

value-comparator.description: Apply a custom comparison algorithm to compare model-value and values contains in the items prop.
value-comparator.description_zh: 应用自定义比较算法来比较 model-value 和 items prop 中包含的值。

variant.description: Applies a distinct style to the component.
variant.description_zh: 将不同的样式应用于组件。

width.description: Sets the width for the component.
